high_descs: Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near bed.
Pick up tissue box from the bed.
After turning around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the cabinet.
Place tissue box on the cabinet.
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the bed on your right.
Pick up tissue box from the bed.
After turning around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the cabinet.
Place tissue box on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Obtaining tissue box from various locations and arranging them in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the bed
Take a tissue box from the top of the bed
Turn left to reach the cabinet
Open the cabinet and put the tissue box inside of it and close the cabinet
Turn right and little bit move towards the bed
Take a tissue box from the top of the bed
Turn left to reach the cabinet again
Open the cabinet and put the tissue box along with the first tissue box and close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the tissue box in the cabinet

high_descs: Go straight and turn right and walk towards the bed.
Pick up the center tissue box out of three from the bed.
Turn left towards the cabinet.
Put the tissue box in the last rack of the cabinet.
Turn back and walk, then turn left towards the bed.
Pick up the right side tissue box from the bed.
Turn left and head to the cabinet.
Put the second tissue box in the right side of the first tissue box into the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put two tissue boxes into the cabinet.
